summary: I am Arno Hoefnagels, I was born in Amersfoort and now living in Utrecht. I am 24 years old and currently a PhD Candidate at Utrecht University. I am very curious and always eager to learn new things, especially about math, science and philosophy. Furthermore, I enjoy playing guitar, playing sports, and diving deep into whatever piques my fancy which includes programming, chess, cooking and much more.
